    "description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>进化你的豆怪！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >豆怪获得经验和进化可解锁额外攻击。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/3db5c25d1870b04f6a66ff8e1fa55981.poster.avif?t=1759168454\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/3db5c25d1870b04f6a66ff8e1fa55981.webm?t=1759168454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/3db5c25d1870b04f6a66ff8e1fa55981.mp4?t=1759168454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>使用强大技能！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种豆怪都有独特的特殊技能和次要攻击。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/f1d19dde4170ec5ee245e5f2b51a569d.poster.avif?t=1759168454\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/f1d19dde4170ec5ee245e5f2b51a569d.webm?t=1759168454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/f1d19dde4170ec5ee245e5f2b51a569d.mp4?t=1759168454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级你的陷阱！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择最适合你策略的路径。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/a9869444059719c5c35a306e0957ca81.poster.avif?t=1759168454\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/a9869444059719c5c35a306e0957ca81.webm?t=1759168454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/a9869444059719c5c35a306e0957ca81.mp4?t=1759168454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>重新规划敌人路线！</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用墙壁来随意改变敌人路线。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/3b74621a86e9ccd7a52eff1b079cd5ad.poster.avif?t=1759168454\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/3b74621a86e9ccd7a52eff1b079cd5ad.webm?t=1759168454\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3059510/extras/3b74621a86e9ccd7a52eff1b079cd5ad.mp4?t=1759168454\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 10种独特豆怪，每种有3个进化阶段。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 12种独特陷阱，每种有2条升级路径。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 21项玩家触发的技能，包括5项召唤。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 40个精心制作的关卡，跨越5个生物群落。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 8场史诗级头目遭遇战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 还有8张无尽模式地图。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 每通过一个关卡，即可解锁新的豆怪、陷阱或升级。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 4种难度选择，从新手模式到豆怪模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 超过50种不同的敌人挑战你的战术技能。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 2种伤害类型，5种伤害元素和7种状态效果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 利用物理和重力来推开你的对手。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 自定义音乐、艺术品和丰富音效。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
